Fast Prochot disabling chicken bit, this is a design driven requirment, not architectural;

                 * 0 - Fast_Prochot_PXYnnnL active behaviour according to spec.
                 * 1 - Fast_Prochot_PXYnnnL == 0. (ie: feature is disabled)
